title: Pullback of the Levi-Civita connection
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Let $$(N,g)$$ be a Riemannian manifold with [[Levi-Civita connection]] $$\nabla$$ and let $$f\colon M\to N$$ be a diffeomorphism. Define the pullback $$f^*\nabla$$ of $$\nabla$$ by

$$
(f^*\nabla)_X Y\coloneqq f^{-1}_*(\nabla_{f_* X} f_* Y)
$$

For $$X,Y\in\mathfrak X(M).$$ Then $$f^*\nabla$$ is the Levi-Civita connection on $$(M,f^*g).$$